This is the email an admin recieves when a user upgrades/downgrades their account and the admin isn't notified during the upgrade/downgrade process for any other reason.  It just makes sure that the admin knows someone upgraded.<br />
<br />
<b>Template Variables:</b><br />
%USER% - Client's username<br />
%NEWPLAN% - The plan the user upgraded/downgraded to<br />
%OLDPLAN% - The plan the user upgraded/downgraded from
